snippet.title: URAGUN - Launch Trailer (Early Access)
snippet.description:
► GET IT ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/724000?utm_source=yt&utm_campaign=launch&utm_medium=yt

Uragun is an action-packed, futuristic top-down shooter. Play as a deadly-but-adorable mech unit and improvise your way out of trouble.

Contact for media/creators: contact[at]kool2play.com

► FB: https://www.facebook.com/UragunGame/
► Twitter: https://twitter.com/UragunGame
► Discord: https://discord.gg/z6rJm8e
► WWW: https://www.kool2play.com

Trailer by: Dash Dot Creations
